{"tid":1921251,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"NBA to suspend season following Wednesday's games","createTime":"2020-03-12T01:42:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T02:18:25.000Z","uid":186,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3f853ce5fbb045a96b1a7ec29ae9ed46cfb168a6","tid":1921251,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T01:42:45.000Z","msg":"NBA to suspend season following Wednesday's games<br />\nOfficial release<br />\nMar 11, 2020 9:37 PM ET<br />\n<br />\nNEW YORK -- The NBA announced that a player on the Utah Jazz has preliminarily tested positive for COVID-19.  The test result was reported shortly prior to the tip-off of tonight&rsquo;s game between the Jazz and Oklahoma City Thunder at Chesapeake Energy Arena.  At that time, tonight&rsquo;s game was canceled.  The affected player was not in the arena.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nba.com/article/2020/03/11/nba-suspend-season-following-wednesdays-games\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nba.com%2Farticle%2F2020%2F03%2F11%2Fnba-suspend-season-following-wednesdays-games&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=d3921642\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nba.com/article/2020/03/11/nba-suspend-season-following-wednesdays-games</a>"},{"pid":"2740dfa1fe7926fd727a005f31ccfe4cb836f5ca","tid":1921251,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T01:42:52.000Z","msg":"NEW YORK -- The NBA announced that a player on the Utah Jazz has preliminarily tested positive for COVID-19.  The test result was reported shortly prior to the tip-off of tonight&rsquo;s game between the Jazz and Oklahoma City Thunder at Chesapeake Energy Arena.  At that time, tonight&rsquo;s game was canceled.  The affected player was not in the arena.<br />\n <br />\nThe NBA is suspending game play following the conclusion of tonight&rsquo;s schedule of games until further notice.  The NBA will use this hiatus to determine next steps for moving forward in regard to the coronavirus pandemic."},{"pid":"4f86d6245c5afd764215aa22fa0eb1c62ad19ab8","tid":1921251,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T01:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc8980eb4f908aa04a5793f31218ccf07ffe111","tid":1921251,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T01:48:07.000Z","msg":"NBA <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5fabf54fe53a6450113635c484f5dde89d63e96","tid":1921251,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T01:49:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5084df295b707880f490257e770a3cc67163231","tid":1921251,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T01:50:02.000Z","msg":"當當年罷工一樣處理"},{"pid":"a64342d6d4e5615f9b30a1e946557d545699ff28","tid":1921251,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T01:50:23.000Z","msg":"買咗nba 點算"},{"pid":"c8675d33ab2767dcbf20adb06d5da7edb706a5a5","tid":1921251,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5084df295b707880f490257e770a3cc67163231","tid":1921251,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T01:50:02.000Z","msg":"當當年罷工一樣處理"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T01:50:38.000Z","msg":"會點處理？"},{"pid":"7b6f1e962cc651e551ce70eae74b455b7e95b385","tid":1921251,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0